SOURCE: https://github.com/software-mansion/react-native-reanimated/blob/main/packages/docs-reanimated/versioned_docs/version-3.x/fundamentals/handling-gestures.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
const tap = Gesture.Tap()
  .onBegin(() => {
    isPressed.value = true;
  })
  .onFinalize(() => {
    isPressed.value = false;
  });

const animatedStyles = useAnimatedStyle(() => ({
  backgroundColor: isPressed.value ? 'yellow' : 'violet',
  transform: [{ scale: withTiming(isPressed.value ? 1.2 : 1) }],
}));

return (
  <GestureDetector gesture={tap}>
    <Animated.View style={[styles.ball, animatedStyles]} />
  </GestureDetector>
);
```

