TITLE: Type Definitions for Custom Layout Transition in React Native Reanimated
DESCRIPTION: This snippet provides TypeScript type definitions for custom layout transitions in React Native Reanimated, including LayoutAnimation, LayoutAnimationsValues, and related types.
