TITLE: Debounce Function Implementation for Performance
DESCRIPTION: A utility function that throttles the execution of scroll event handlers to improve performance by reducing the number of calculations performed during rapid scrolling.
SOURCE: https://github.com/software-mansion/react-native-reanimated/blob/main/packages/docs-reanimated/blog/section-list.md#2025-04-16_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function debounce(fn, ms) {
  'worklet';
  let timeout;
  return (...args) => {
    'worklet';
    if (timeout) {
      cancelAnimation(timeout);
    }
    timeout = setTimeout(() => fn(...args), ms);
  };
}
```

